Diane Tuckman bụ onye America na-ese ihe
A maara ya maka ọrụ ya na-ise ihe n'ákwà silk, yana dịka onye dere ọtụtụ akwụkwọ gbasara isiokwu ahụ na Jan Janas. Ọ bi ma na-arụ ọrụ na Lanham, Maryland na mpaghara Greater Washington, D.C.
N'ajụjụ ọnụ ya na The Washington Free Beacon, Tuckman chetara na mgbe ọ bi n'Ijipt dị ka nwatakịrị n'oge WWII, ha na-agba ụmụ agbọghọ ndị Juu égbè n'okporo ámá..
Mụ na ezinụlọ m gbapụrụ na 1948 wee gaa France

Ọ bụ ezie na ọ bụghị ihe na-agbawa obi, ọbụna na France bụ oge siri ike mgbe agha ahụ gasịrị, na ike oke tiketi na obere ụlọ. Tuckman kwagara United States na 1958 n'oge na-adịghị anya mgbe ọ lụsịrị di

A na-ekwu na Tuckman bụ otu n'ime ndị na-ese ihe na-enyere aka mee ka ihe osise silk na United States site na akwụkwọ ya, na mgbe ụlọ ọrụ ya (Ivy Imports) bụ ụlọ ọrụ US mbụ "na-ebubata ihe osise French dị mkpa iji see na silk".

Tuckman bụkwa onye guzobere otu Silk Painters International (SPIN), nke bụ otu na-anaghị achọ uru, nke nyere aka ịhazi Nzukọ nke Abụọ nke International Silk Painting Congress na Mahadum George Mason n'afọ 2000. SPIN ugbu a na-ahazi ihe osise silk ugboro abụọ; nke kachasị ọhụrụ emere na 2018 na Gatlinburg, TN. Nzukọ ahụ nwere ihe karịrị ndị otu narị ise ugbu a.

Tuckman egosila ma hazie ihe ngosi nka silk na gburugburu mpaghara Greater Washington, DC. A na-akpọ ya "onye ọsụ ụzọ na-ese ihe silk na America, ọ na-akụzi, na-ese, ma na-egosipụta ihe osise silk nke ya, yana ịkwalite ụdị nka site na mmemme agụmakwụkwọ ya
